02c60a4ff267b7d010daf4ea6dfba380b6a2c377:
query GetBid($bidId: String!) {
  bidByBidId(bidId: $bidId) {
    bidId
    auctionAddress
    auctionName
    bundleHash
    replacedBy
    signer
    signature
    status
    submittedTimestamp
    statusLastUpdated
    tipRevealed
    txHash
    amount
    auctionByAuctionAddressAndAuctionName {
      price
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
